### Create notification setting
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notification-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "Seoul",
  "uvThreshold": 6,
  "enabled": true
}

### Get notification settings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notification-settings

### Create notification setting with blank region
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notification-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "",
  "uvThreshold": 6,
  "enabled": true
}

### Create notification setting with invalid threshold
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notification-settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "Seoul",
  "uvThreshold": -1,
  "enabled": true
}